p: The essential oil and the main compounds exhibited fumigant and contact toxicity. In addition to the three isolated compounds, some existing data for the other three monoterpenoids (4-terpineol, α-terpineol, and γ-terpinene) that we identified in this essential oil were also listed here to compare their effects to control L. serricorne adults. Their structures are shown in Figure 2. Thus, the data of the six compounds and the essential oil, as well as the positive controls, are shown in Table 2.
